LISP Networking module

To use this library you should install the following:

    - python 2.6
    - virtualenv 2.6
    - scapy 2.2.0-dev
   
MacOSX Guide:

- install macports ( obtain the software here http://www.macports.org/ )
    $ git clone https://job@github.com/intouch/py-lispnetworking.git
    $ cd py-lispnetworking
    $ sudo port install python26 py26-virtualenv libdnet py26-libdnet
    $ virtualenv-2.6 .
    $ source bin/activate
    $ pip install pcapy hg+http://hg.secdev.org/scapy yolk

eventueel: pip install libpcap



Ubuntu Guide:

    Setup virtualenv and python

        $ sudo apt-get install libxslt1-dev libxml2-dev python-virtualenv python-pip python-dev python2.6

    Install git-core

        $ sudo apt-get install git-core

    Clone repo from github.com

        $ git clone https://job@github.com/intouch/py-lispnetworking.git

    Enter project directory and setup virtualenv

        $ cd py-lispnetworking
        $ virtualenv-2.6 .
        $ source bin/activate
        $ pip install pcapy hg+http://hg.secdev.org/scapy yolk


